snippet.title: Edumarketing
snippet.description:
Hello, my name is Ginger, founder of Edumarketing.com.  Welcome to our channel! I’m an education specialist, author, entrepreneur and marketing strategist who helps business owners create educational marketing content. I love combining information with tech, to create powerful marketing systems. I also offer education marketing coaching and consulting. Want to learn more about how I can help you become more successful or grow your online business? Just visit www.edumarketing.com

When I’m not helping my clients create educational marketing content for their businesses, I’m spending time with my husband exploring new places, traveling, and cooking delicious food.
